WEBVTT

01:30.810 --> 01:35.030
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.800 --> 01:39.380
[2003]

01:42.000 --> 01:43.070
Where do you think you're going?

01:43.070 --> 01:43.789
Because of you,

01:43.789 --> 01:45.229
my mom scolds me every day,

01:45.229 --> 01:46.830
telling me to learn from you.

01:46.950 --> 01:48.410
What's so great about you?

01:48.560 --> 01:50.479
Think you're special
just because you have no parents?

01:50.479 --> 01:52.509
You think you can
get into an elite high school?

01:52.509 --> 01:52.870
Yeah.

01:53.120 --> 01:55.039
You think you can
get into an elite high school?

01:55.039 --> 01:56.070
Why bother taking the exam?

01:56.070 --> 01:56.870
Don't take it!

01:57.200 --> 01:58.000
Give it back!

02:01.000 --> 02:02.920
Such diligent notes.

02:03.310 --> 02:04.240
Don't tear them!

02:04.310 --> 02:05.230
Don't!

02:10.190 --> 02:12.150
Make sure you do well on the exam.

02:32.240 --> 02:32.970
Does it hurt?

02:33.470 --> 02:33.910
Yes.

02:35.079 --> 02:37.079
Since you've already felt the pain,

02:37.150 --> 02:38.550
all the more you must win.

02:43.800 --> 02:47.190
[Episode 7: No Matter How Much the Pain,
You Must Win]

02:52.590 --> 02:53.000
No.

02:54.800 --> 02:55.930
I'm taking the exam.

02:57.240 --> 02:58.640
This was not an accident.

02:59.470 --> 03:00.120
Xiaolan.

03:00.360 --> 03:00.800
Mom.

03:01.130 --> 03:02.390
This is not your fault.

03:02.470 --> 03:03.730
They did it on purpose.

03:13.800 --> 03:14.330
Brother.

03:14.600 --> 03:16.370
Why isn't Zhang Cui here yet?

03:17.630 --> 03:18.960
What would she be here for?

03:18.960 --> 03:20.220
To cause more trouble?

03:22.190 --> 03:22.910
How did things

03:22.910 --> 03:24.079
turn out like this?

03:24.310 --> 03:25.590
Before I could even react,

03:25.590 --> 03:27.240
everyone just crowded in.

03:27.360 --> 03:28.310
Xiaolan's hand

03:28.310 --> 03:29.750
won't be disabled, right?

03:29.750 --> 03:31.150
H-How is that possible?

03:31.590 --> 03:32.030
I mean.

03:32.520 --> 03:33.150
Maybe...

03:34.520 --> 03:36.079
Maybe we should go up and check.

03:36.079 --> 03:36.630
Are you crazy?

03:36.630 --> 03:38.760
You'll just cause trouble if you go up.

03:40.280 --> 03:40.800
Dajun,

03:41.710 --> 03:43.310
why don't you go up and check?

03:43.310 --> 03:44.750
You are her biological father, after all.

03:44.750 --> 03:45.520
Stop it.

03:46.430 --> 03:48.000
Xiaolan won't acknowledge me.

03:48.000 --> 03:49.260
If it weren't for you guys last time...

03:49.260 --> 03:50.030
No, no.

03:50.520 --> 03:51.000
Dajun,

03:51.470 --> 03:52.800
don't blame me for this.

03:53.030 --> 03:54.680
I didn't instigate this.

03:55.000 --> 03:55.360
Right?

03:55.360 --> 03:56.310
I-I was trying to

03:56.310 --> 03:57.560
stop the fight the whole time.

03:57.560 --> 03:58.079
Dajun.

03:59.079 --> 04:01.140
Let me say a few words as your brother.

04:01.520 --> 04:02.360
That Liu Fen

04:02.560 --> 04:03.680
asked for a divorce from you

04:03.680 --> 04:04.960
in front of so many people.

04:04.960 --> 04:05.960
It's outrageous.

04:06.240 --> 04:06.800
Tell me,

04:07.120 --> 04:08.320
what do you plan to do?

04:11.590 --> 04:12.720
What does that mean?

04:14.910 --> 04:16.370
Don't look at me, Brother.

04:16.560 --> 04:18.220
This has nothing to do with me.

04:20.899 --> 04:21.959
You two... this...

04:22.160 --> 04:22.870
No.

04:23.040 --> 04:24.770
Your hand is a lifelong matter.

04:24.950 --> 04:25.600
Xiaolan.

04:25.800 --> 04:27.040
You have to listen to your mom

04:27.040 --> 04:28.270
and the doctor this time.

04:28.270 --> 04:29.750
I hope you can get good grades

04:29.750 --> 04:31.190
and bring honor to No.1 High School.

04:31.190 --> 04:32.040
But we can't,

04:32.040 --> 04:33.040
just for one exam,

04:33.040 --> 04:34.240
ruin your whole life.

04:34.600 --> 04:35.360
Your health

04:35.360 --> 04:36.630
is more important than anything.

04:36.630 --> 04:38.159
We can take the exam next year.

04:38.159 --> 04:39.040
I don't even know

04:39.040 --> 04:40.440
if I'll be here next year.

04:43.750 --> 04:44.360
Mr. Sun.

04:45.130 --> 04:47.190
Unexpected things happen every year.

04:47.190 --> 04:48.390
If I take it next year,

04:48.430 --> 04:49.120
I might not get

04:49.120 --> 04:50.120
the same results.

04:50.690 --> 04:52.240
Even if you don't pass next year,

04:52.240 --> 04:53.480
I can't watch you

04:53.480 --> 04:54.950
ruin your hand.

04:55.630 --> 04:56.270
Xiaolan.

04:56.950 --> 04:58.680
You should think it over again.

04:58.870 --> 04:59.430
Mr. Sun.

05:00.080 --> 05:00.560
Mom.

05:01.160 --> 05:02.290
I've made up my mind.

05:02.780 --> 05:05.440
I must take
the college entrance exam this year.

05:09.720 --> 05:12.180
It's okay.
You don't have to keep holding it.

05:12.340 --> 05:12.830
Don't move.

05:12.830 --> 05:16.030
-The doctor doesn't allow you...
-They're finally back.

05:16.750 --> 05:19.140
Mrs. Chen came back
but couldn't explain it clearly.

05:19.140 --> 05:19.670
Your uncle

05:19.670 --> 05:21.390
insisted I stay home
so I wouldn't cause trouble.

05:21.390 --> 05:22.390
I was so worried.

05:22.870 --> 05:23.330
This...

05:23.480 --> 05:24.600
Your hand is bandaged up like this.

05:24.600 --> 05:25.680
How will you take the exam?

05:25.680 --> 05:26.280
It's fine.

05:26.480 --> 05:28.040
The doctor said I can still write.

05:28.040 --> 05:30.040
It still hurts even if you can write.

05:30.160 --> 05:32.220
The doctor prescribed painkillers.

05:32.430 --> 05:33.430
It's all my fault.

05:33.950 --> 05:35.550
I'm the one who hurt Xiaolan.

05:35.600 --> 05:37.240
All right, let's talk inside.

05:37.240 --> 05:37.720
Right.

05:37.870 --> 05:38.800
Let's go inside.

05:42.040 --> 05:42.720
Let's go.

05:48.480 --> 05:49.000
Mom.

05:49.310 --> 05:50.570
Don't blame yourself.

05:51.159 --> 05:52.360
You did great today.

05:52.950 --> 05:54.390
You were so confident

05:54.600 --> 05:56.040
when you went on the stage.

05:56.040 --> 05:56.680
I know.

05:57.190 --> 05:58.120
Actually, every step you took

05:58.120 --> 05:59.159
was really difficult

05:59.159 --> 06:00.040
for you.

06:01.560 --> 06:03.490
I was just holding it together too.

06:04.680 --> 06:06.140
I couldn't embarrass you.

06:06.200 --> 06:06.960
You didn't.

06:07.720 --> 06:09.240
And you said you wanted

06:09.480 --> 06:10.480
a divorce in front of so many people

06:10.480 --> 06:11.880
at the school gate today.

06:11.920 --> 06:12.920
That takes a lot

06:12.920 --> 06:13.920
of courage.

06:14.870 --> 06:16.130
Mom, thank you so much.

06:16.750 --> 06:17.480
I know

06:17.830 --> 06:19.120
you were trying your hardest

06:19.120 --> 06:19.920
to protect me.

06:22.190 --> 06:23.360
Mr. Sun told me

06:23.950 --> 06:26.280
you can get into a really good university.

06:26.560 --> 06:28.160
He told me to protect you well

06:28.560 --> 06:31.020
so you could take
the exam with peace of mind.

06:32.110 --> 06:33.430
But I failed.

06:33.680 --> 06:34.870
If I had divorced him sooner,

06:34.870 --> 06:36.870
he wouldn't have come for you today.

06:38.630 --> 06:39.120
Mom.

06:40.360 --> 06:41.760
I really don't blame you.

06:42.040 --> 06:43.750
Even if you had divorced him sooner,

06:43.750 --> 06:45.480
he still would have come today.

06:46.070 --> 06:47.240
They just don't want me

06:47.240 --> 06:48.700
to take the exam smoothly.

06:54.040 --> 06:54.370
Yong.

06:54.380 --> 06:54.710
Move.

06:54.720 --> 06:55.430
What are you doing?

06:55.430 --> 06:56.800
I'll kill those darn Xias—

06:56.800 --> 06:57.310
Uncle!

06:58.310 --> 06:59.840
You kill him, and then what?

07:00.040 --> 07:02.120
He goes to the hospital,
and you go to court?

07:02.120 --> 07:02.680
But we can't just

07:02.680 --> 07:04.120
let those bastards off the hook!

07:04.120 --> 07:04.560
Uncle.

07:05.190 --> 07:06.390
Do I look like someone

07:06.430 --> 07:07.890
who doesn't take revenge?

07:08.240 --> 07:09.240
It's just not now.

07:09.920 --> 07:12.070
The exam
is the most important thing right now.

07:12.070 --> 07:12.870
Yes, Yong.

07:13.240 --> 07:15.040
Xiaolan is about to take her exam.

07:15.040 --> 07:16.800
Don't cause any more trouble.

07:17.000 --> 07:17.530
Alright.

07:18.430 --> 07:19.920
I underestimated Xia Ziyu

07:19.920 --> 07:21.650
and her family's viciousness.

07:21.940 --> 07:22.450
But now,

07:22.480 --> 07:23.740
since we're prepared,

07:24.040 --> 07:25.840
we won't let them succeed again.

07:31.040 --> 07:32.100
What are you doing?

07:32.610 --> 07:33.830
I'm going to slaughter a chicken

07:33.830 --> 07:35.159
to give Xiaolan a boost.

07:41.390 --> 07:42.250
It's okay, Mom.

07:45.430 --> 07:46.030
It's fine.

07:52.480 --> 07:53.970
Fen, have some water.

07:54.120 --> 07:54.480
Yong.

08:01.830 --> 08:03.750
About divorcing Xia Dajun,

08:04.480 --> 08:05.940
have you made up your mind?

08:09.630 --> 08:10.120
Yong.

08:11.190 --> 08:12.270
Xiaolan and I

08:13.100 --> 08:13.980
have moved out

08:14.010 --> 08:15.250
for a long time now.

08:17.390 --> 08:18.680
I'm just slow.

08:19.240 --> 08:21.370
My mind doesn't work as fast as others.

08:22.270 --> 08:23.920
You told me back then

08:24.950 --> 08:26.550
that if I left the Xia family,

08:26.920 --> 08:28.750
things would definitely get better.

08:28.750 --> 08:30.070
I believed you.

08:30.800 --> 08:31.390
But

08:32.669 --> 08:34.510
I didn't really feel it myself.

08:38.030 --> 08:39.120
Life just went on,

08:39.120 --> 08:40.750
day by day.

08:41.549 --> 08:42.240
I didn't feel like

08:42.240 --> 08:43.770
anything had changed much.

08:44.510 --> 08:46.000
But looking back today,

08:49.670 --> 08:50.510
I realize

08:51.150 --> 08:52.320
that Xia Dajun and I

08:53.320 --> 08:55.380
stopped being family a long time ago.

08:57.360 --> 08:58.080
Sis.

08:59.320 --> 09:00.850
Actually, you're not slow.

09:02.270 --> 09:03.440
You're just naive.

09:05.030 --> 09:06.630
It's because I'm naive

09:06.630 --> 09:08.270
that I almost hurt Xiaolan.

09:09.200 --> 09:10.120
It's never too late

09:10.120 --> 09:11.320
to figure things out.

09:11.880 --> 09:12.910
Since you've decided,

09:12.910 --> 09:14.480
I'll go find Wangda right away.

09:14.480 --> 09:15.440
I'll ask him to help,

09:15.440 --> 09:16.640
so it would be faster.

09:18.080 --> 09:19.120
When it's done,

09:20.270 --> 09:22.390
Xiaolan can study in peace.

09:24.610 --> 09:26.210
[Divorce Certificate]

09:24.870 --> 09:25.720
It's done.

09:27.080 --> 09:28.790
Wangda went with them.

09:28.960 --> 09:30.160
It was done in no time.

09:30.200 --> 09:32.550
The Civil Affairs Bureau
has it on file too.

09:32.550 --> 09:33.720
As for your household registrations,

09:33.720 --> 09:35.120
I've transferred them back.

09:35.120 --> 09:36.390
Getting letters of introduction

09:36.390 --> 09:37.450
will be easier now.

09:38.380 --> 09:39.600
The village also promised

09:39.600 --> 09:41.130
to allocate land to you two.

09:41.720 --> 09:42.790
From now on,

09:43.080 --> 09:45.410
you have nothing to do
with the Xia family.

09:46.480 --> 09:47.030
Fen.

09:47.390 --> 09:48.450
That's great news.

09:48.720 --> 09:50.360
Thank heavens for this.

09:50.750 --> 09:51.240
Today,

09:51.400 --> 09:52.720
we have to eat something good

09:52.720 --> 09:54.030
and celebrate properly.

09:54.030 --> 09:55.240
I'll go cook now.

09:57.120 --> 09:57.630
Mom.

09:58.840 --> 09:59.570
You're free.

10:00.360 --> 10:01.270
A new life

10:01.480 --> 10:02.540
is waiting for you.

10:11.910 --> 10:13.440
Good heavens!

10:14.550 --> 10:17.550
I've failed my ancestors

10:17.550 --> 10:18.910
by giving birth to this

10:18.910 --> 10:20.600
useless thing.

10:21.270 --> 10:22.960
What a complete embarrassment

10:22.960 --> 10:27.440
to the Xia family!

10:28.630 --> 10:29.600
Dajun

10:29.840 --> 10:32.240
just watched his wife

10:32.580 --> 10:35.110
divorce him and move her registration.

10:35.360 --> 10:36.630
The worst part is,

10:36.630 --> 10:38.600
she's even taking our land

10:38.600 --> 10:39.670
away with her.

10:40.150 --> 10:42.720
Is there no justice left?

10:44.910 --> 10:45.690
Xia Dajun.

10:46.150 --> 10:46.760
Can't you,

10:46.790 --> 10:47.630
just for once,

10:47.630 --> 10:48.870
use your brain?

10:49.510 --> 10:50.570
Look for yourself.

10:50.600 --> 10:51.550
Am I better off now

10:51.550 --> 10:53.150
or when I was in the Xia family?

10:53.150 --> 10:54.030
Is there anyone in that family

10:54.030 --> 10:54.740
who wants the best for me

10:54.740 --> 10:55.740
or my mother?

10:56.150 --> 10:56.750
Xia Dajun.

10:57.910 --> 10:58.960
I want a divorce.

11:01.930 --> 11:02.720
Dajun.

11:03.750 --> 11:05.630
Are you even a man?

11:09.270 --> 11:10.910
You're a spineless coward

11:10.910 --> 11:13.200
who can't even control your wife.

11:13.480 --> 11:15.200
You coward!

11:22.390 --> 11:24.200
Hey, you...

11:24.790 --> 11:25.920
Where are you going?

11:26.790 --> 11:27.910
You're useless,

11:27.910 --> 11:29.370
and you won't let me say it?

11:29.670 --> 11:31.070
I haven't said two words,

11:31.200 --> 11:32.870
and you pull a long face,

11:32.870 --> 11:33.670
lift your legs,

11:33.670 --> 11:35.510
and walk out?

11:35.870 --> 11:37.930
If you walk out of the Xia house today,

11:38.030 --> 11:38.480
you...

11:38.480 --> 11:40.000
god knows where you'll end up,

11:40.000 --> 11:40.960
I'm telling you!

12:27.000 --> 12:27.440
Mom.

12:30.840 --> 12:31.370
Xiaolan.

12:40.840 --> 12:41.760
Tell me,

12:44.000 --> 12:45.400
did I really get divorced

12:46.320 --> 12:47.320
just like that?

12:51.030 --> 12:52.120
Xia Dajun

12:53.970 --> 12:56.100
won't cause any more trouble, will he?

13:00.870 --> 13:01.360
Mom.

13:02.270 --> 13:03.000
Don't worry.

13:03.960 --> 13:04.720
Our household register

13:04.720 --> 13:05.790
has been moved out.

13:06.820 --> 13:08.420
From now on, you're no longer

13:08.750 --> 13:09.790
the Xia family daughter-in-law

13:09.790 --> 13:10.600
who was looked down upon

13:10.600 --> 13:11.730
for not having a son.

13:13.030 --> 13:14.360
You are your own person.

13:21.480 --> 13:22.750
In all these years,

13:23.840 --> 13:26.970
this is the first time
you've said no to Xia Dajun, right?

13:29.390 --> 13:30.150
It is.

13:31.030 --> 13:31.790
Before,

13:33.240 --> 13:35.100
I listened to him for everything.

13:35.670 --> 13:36.630
And before that,

13:37.900 --> 13:40.160
I listened to your uncle for everything.

13:41.630 --> 13:42.030
Mom.

13:42.750 --> 13:43.550
From now on,

13:44.150 --> 13:46.150
you should listen to yourself more.

13:46.440 --> 13:47.840
Think about what you want,

13:47.840 --> 13:49.100
and what you want to do.

13:49.510 --> 13:51.170
Before making any decisions,

13:51.670 --> 13:53.360
consider your own feelings.

13:55.480 --> 13:56.240
From now on, we don't have to

13:56.240 --> 13:57.630
please anyone.

13:58.870 --> 14:00.530
You can live the life you want.

14:02.750 --> 14:03.750
I can't do that.

14:04.510 --> 14:06.170
I still have to look after you.

14:09.600 --> 14:11.600
If I wasn't so worried about you,

14:12.240 --> 14:13.440
I wouldn't have dared

14:14.610 --> 14:15.850
to say those things.

14:21.270 --> 14:21.720
Mom.

14:24.670 --> 14:25.200
Why?

14:28.210 --> 14:28.810
Nothing.

14:33.910 --> 14:35.030
It's just that...

14:36.600 --> 14:38.000
it's so good to have a mom.

14:40.580 --> 14:41.370
I'm so happy.

14:45.510 --> 14:46.390
Silly child.

14:50.120 --> 14:51.320
This honest woman

14:51.600 --> 14:53.860
lived in the Xia family for over 20 years.

14:54.720 --> 14:56.510
She spent more years with the Xias

14:56.510 --> 14:57.630
than with the Lius.

14:58.870 --> 15:01.070
God knows how much courage she mustered

15:01.510 --> 15:03.240
to finally ask for a divorce.

15:04.840 --> 15:06.670
She's so good to Xia Xiaolan.

15:08.910 --> 15:09.970
She's so good to me.

15:16.770 --> 15:17.720
One hundred points.

15:17.720 --> 15:20.120
Eat this
and you'll score a hundred points.

15:20.120 --> 15:21.650
That's just superstition.

15:21.670 --> 15:22.600
Besides,
full marks for the college entrance exam

15:22.600 --> 15:23.530
isn't a hundred.

15:24.200 --> 15:24.960
It's just for good luck.

15:24.960 --> 15:25.720
Bend it,

15:25.750 --> 15:26.870
and it becomes 700.

15:27.080 --> 15:27.680
All right.

15:27.910 --> 15:28.770
Good luck, Son.

15:29.960 --> 15:30.360
Okay.

15:30.440 --> 15:30.870
I'll try

15:30.870 --> 15:32.390
for that 700 points of yours.

15:32.390 --> 15:32.850
I'm off.

15:33.000 --> 15:33.750
Don't be careless.

15:33.750 --> 15:34.880
Wait for my triumph.

15:42.240 --> 15:42.960
Don't be nervous,

15:42.960 --> 15:43.440
Mrs. Chen.

15:43.440 --> 15:45.100
Check everything carefully.

15:45.320 --> 15:45.920
Chen Qing.

15:46.150 --> 15:46.680
Xiaolan.

15:47.200 --> 15:48.390
You'll do great.

15:49.550 --> 15:50.480
Don't be nervous.

15:50.480 --> 15:51.120
Right.

15:52.320 --> 15:53.670
Do you have everything?

15:54.080 --> 15:55.120
Did you bring your rulers?

15:55.120 --> 15:55.630
Yes.

15:55.690 --> 16:01.990
[Hedong No.3 High School]

15:55.870 --> 15:57.200
I brought my rulers and pens.

15:57.200 --> 15:58.850
Keep your exam permit safe later.

15:58.850 --> 15:59.260
Okay.

15:59.910 --> 16:01.970
Candidates, please enter the venue.

16:04.960 --> 16:06.360
Xiaolan, mind your hand.

16:06.440 --> 16:06.840
Okay.

16:07.320 --> 16:07.980
Uncle, Mom.

16:08.270 --> 16:09.080
Don't worry.

16:09.270 --> 16:10.960
I'll give you a surprise.

16:12.150 --> 16:12.750
Good luck.

16:27.120 --> 16:27.750
Students.

16:28.720 --> 16:30.180
The exam is about to begin.

16:30.550 --> 16:32.680
Please read every question carefully

16:32.750 --> 16:34.010
and answer carefully.

16:34.200 --> 16:35.600
No talking to each other.

16:35.960 --> 16:37.840
It is now time for the Chinese exam.

16:37.840 --> 16:39.570
Please observe the exam rules.

16:45.150 --> 16:46.360
The exam begins now.

16:46.790 --> 16:48.480
You may start writing.

16:51.470 --> 16:53.200
[1984 University Recruitment
Zhou Cheng]

17:13.640 --> 17:14.240
Finally,

17:14.930 --> 17:15.660
you're here.

17:30.920 --> 17:31.920
Xiaolan.

17:32.030 --> 17:33.610
Math was so hard.

17:33.680 --> 17:35.610
I definitely won't pass this year.

17:35.790 --> 17:37.120
Math was just a bit hard,

17:37.160 --> 17:38.680
and you're already giving up?

17:38.680 --> 17:40.310
Do well in the remaining subjects,

17:40.310 --> 17:41.480
and you'll still get into

17:41.480 --> 17:42.400
the university you deserve to.

17:42.400 --> 17:43.720
If even Xiaolan thinks it's hard,

17:43.720 --> 17:44.980
then it really is hard.

17:45.070 --> 17:46.070
Since it's hard for everyone,

17:46.070 --> 17:46.930
then it's okay.

17:47.030 --> 17:47.960
We can't give up.

17:48.480 --> 17:49.510
-Don't give up.
-Come on!

17:49.510 --> 17:50.160
-Come on!
-Come on!

17:50.160 --> 17:51.720
[Foreign Language]

18:04.680 --> 18:06.080
The English exam begins.

18:27.510 --> 18:29.770
-It's finally done.
-It's finally done.

18:35.550 --> 18:36.000
Uncle.

18:36.240 --> 18:37.170
How's your hand?

18:37.480 --> 18:38.080
It's fine.

18:38.310 --> 18:38.790
Tell me,

18:39.070 --> 18:40.640
if I get into the best university,

18:40.640 --> 18:41.800
how should we celebrate?

18:41.800 --> 18:43.070
We'll treat the whole village to a meal.

18:43.070 --> 18:44.200
For 3 days straight!

18:44.720 --> 18:45.250
Let's go.

18:45.270 --> 18:46.240
Your mom is at Blue Phoenix,

18:46.240 --> 18:47.020
waiting for us to eat.

18:47.020 --> 18:49.240
[Jingcheng Yucai High School]

18:47.070 --> 18:48.110
They're out, right?

18:48.110 --> 18:48.830
You see him?

18:50.070 --> 18:50.580
Cheng!

18:50.720 --> 18:51.510
Here, here.

18:51.550 --> 18:51.920
Mom.

18:52.160 --> 18:52.680
Cheng.

18:53.350 --> 18:54.000
We agreed

18:54.110 --> 18:55.350
we'd celebrate the completion of your exam.

18:55.350 --> 18:55.950
Mrs. Guan,

18:56.510 --> 18:57.680
Cheng is free now, right?

18:57.680 --> 18:58.590
Yes.

18:58.640 --> 18:59.270
Go ahead. Go.

18:59.270 --> 19:00.030
I'm going then, Mom.

19:00.030 --> 19:01.090
Come, give it to me.

19:01.110 --> 19:02.750
Mrs. Guan, we're leaving now.

19:02.750 --> 19:03.750
Be safe.

19:06.110 --> 19:06.710
All right.

19:07.350 --> 19:08.030
Remember,

19:08.880 --> 19:11.080
your answers must not be ambiguous.

19:11.240 --> 19:13.550
Especially for the sections
with many subjective questions,

19:13.550 --> 19:14.440
you must check

19:14.440 --> 19:16.300
if you hit the key scoring points.

19:16.350 --> 19:18.440
Try to estimate your score accurately.

19:18.440 --> 19:20.110
That way, the school can accurately

19:20.110 --> 19:21.480
predict the cutoff scores,

19:21.480 --> 19:22.880
so everyone
can fill out their applications well

19:22.880 --> 19:24.140
and get into a college.

19:28.240 --> 19:28.830
Xiaolan,

19:29.680 --> 19:30.640
is your hand okay?

19:30.640 --> 19:32.040
Let me calculate for you.

19:32.070 --> 19:33.270
It's okay. I can do it.

19:43.000 --> 19:43.530
Xiaolan,

19:43.830 --> 19:45.270
how is your estimate going?

19:45.270 --> 19:46.800
It should be 90 for Chinese.

19:47.070 --> 19:48.350
98 for English.

19:48.590 --> 19:49.450
92 for Physics.

19:49.460 --> 19:50.850
94 for Chemistry.

19:50.880 --> 19:51.920
45 for Biology.

19:52.200 --> 19:53.640
As for Politics...

19:53.960 --> 19:55.030
probably only 50.

19:56.640 --> 19:57.110
Why?

19:57.440 --> 19:58.200
Why is Politics only 50?

19:58.200 --> 19:59.440
After all, my hand is in a cast.

19:59.440 --> 20:00.640
It's not convenient to write,

20:00.640 --> 20:02.370
so I was a bit slow in answering.

20:02.640 --> 20:03.700
That's such a pity.

20:05.080 --> 20:05.790
What about Math?

20:05.790 --> 20:06.790
How much for Math?

20:06.920 --> 20:08.310
Math should be

20:08.590 --> 20:09.590
115.

20:10.420 --> 20:11.350
115?

20:11.550 --> 20:12.350
That high?

20:17.160 --> 20:17.820
Then you...

20:17.960 --> 20:19.560
your total score would be...

20:20.480 --> 20:23.030
The total would be 584.

20:26.070 --> 20:27.030
Xiaolan!

20:28.510 --> 20:29.640
I was just at the door

20:29.800 --> 20:31.030
and heard your estimate was

20:31.030 --> 20:32.270
584 points?

20:32.640 --> 20:33.000
Yes.

20:34.830 --> 20:36.350
Last year, our Yunan Province's

20:36.350 --> 20:36.960
top science scorer

20:36.960 --> 20:38.550
scored exactly 584 points!

20:39.000 --> 20:40.720
Have you decided on your application?

20:40.720 --> 20:42.350
I want to apply to Huaqing University.

20:42.350 --> 20:43.240
But for the specific major,

20:43.240 --> 20:44.500
I haven't decided yet.

20:44.750 --> 20:45.200
Good.

20:45.340 --> 20:45.900
Go back,

20:45.960 --> 20:47.200
and discuss it with your family.

20:47.200 --> 20:48.070
With your score,

20:48.070 --> 20:49.530
you can get into any major.

20:49.830 --> 20:50.360
Consider

20:50.510 --> 20:51.350
economics or finance—

20:51.350 --> 20:52.790
these industries

20:52.790 --> 20:53.880
are rapidly developing now.

20:53.880 --> 20:54.810
Mr. Sun.

20:54.960 --> 20:56.070
Xiaolan is so smart,

20:56.070 --> 20:57.440
let her make her own decision.

20:57.440 --> 20:58.130
Right, right.

20:58.130 --> 20:59.530
You decide for yourself.

21:01.550 --> 21:02.240
Ms. Qi.

21:02.550 --> 21:04.280
This child has finally made it.

21:09.240 --> 21:10.350
Mother, I beg you.

21:10.750 --> 21:12.610
Please give Xiaolan a way to live.

21:12.770 --> 21:14.110
You think the Liu family

21:14.110 --> 21:14.710
has no one?

21:14.880 --> 21:15.920
Who's got nothing better to do

21:15.920 --> 21:17.270
than gossip around here?

21:17.270 --> 21:17.830
What are you doing?

21:17.830 --> 21:19.000
Get your ass over here!

21:19.000 --> 21:21.200
I'll rip that tongue
right out of your big mouth!

21:21.200 --> 21:22.200
Comrade Xiaolan.

21:46.750 --> 21:47.680
Why are you here?

21:58.400 --> 21:59.930
How long have you been here?

22:00.160 --> 22:01.020
For a while now.

22:01.440 --> 22:02.270
I saw you were asleep,

22:02.270 --> 22:03.400
so I didn't wake you.

22:04.030 --> 22:05.030
You dreamt again?

22:05.960 --> 22:06.400
Yeah.

22:07.880 --> 22:08.940
Was it a good dream?

22:09.350 --> 22:10.070
Was I

22:10.590 --> 22:11.200
in it?

22:13.000 --> 22:14.060
It was a good dream.

22:15.280 --> 22:17.520
Because the bad things

22:18.070 --> 22:19.240
are finally over.

22:22.070 --> 22:23.330
Why didn't you tell me?

22:27.160 --> 22:29.020
It's just a minor inconvenience.

22:29.160 --> 22:30.820
I finished the exam, didn't I?

22:32.430 --> 22:33.360
You're in a cast,

22:33.830 --> 22:35.030
taking painkillers,

22:35.030 --> 22:35.890
and had a fever—

22:36.350 --> 22:38.080
you held on like this for 3 days.

22:38.240 --> 22:40.240
You got an infection, fainted,
and were hospitalized—

22:40.240 --> 22:42.300
you call this a minor inconvenience?

22:42.310 --> 22:43.510
It's really nothing.

22:44.760 --> 22:45.350
Why did you insist

22:45.350 --> 22:46.410
on taking the exam?

22:47.550 --> 22:48.550
With your grades,

22:49.110 --> 22:49.750
even if you took it next year,

22:49.750 --> 22:50.880
you'd still do well.

22:51.790 --> 22:53.120
It must've been painful

22:54.270 --> 22:55.130
these few days.

22:57.240 --> 22:58.440
It hurt the most

22:58.440 --> 22:59.640
when I was stepped on.

23:00.200 --> 23:02.060
Since I've already felt the pain,

23:02.240 --> 23:03.640
all the more I have to win.

23:05.270 --> 23:05.750
Look,

23:06.790 --> 23:07.650
I won, didn't I?

23:10.200 --> 23:10.660
And you?

23:11.310 --> 23:13.240
Have you estimated your score yet?

23:13.880 --> 23:15.540
I came to find you right after.

23:15.750 --> 23:16.640
I won

23:16.830 --> 23:17.760
this battle too.

23:18.960 --> 23:19.720
But,

23:20.880 --> 23:22.590
there is a more important battle

23:22.590 --> 23:23.720
coming up.

23:25.030 --> 23:26.110
Whether I win

23:28.000 --> 23:29.200
doesn't depend on me.

23:30.510 --> 23:31.910
With such a handsome face

23:32.400 --> 23:34.270
making such a sweet request,

23:34.720 --> 23:36.200
how could I refuse?

23:37.720 --> 23:38.920
With a second chance at life,

23:38.920 --> 23:40.350
if I just focus on making money,

23:40.350 --> 23:42.080
wouldn't I be wasting my youth?

23:42.410 --> 23:43.240
In terms of sweet love,

23:43.240 --> 23:45.100
I'm going to fall head over heels.

23:45.790 --> 23:46.720
However,

23:49.440 --> 23:51.370
you're in such a rush for an answer?

23:52.350 --> 23:53.880
The results aren't out yet.

23:54.160 --> 23:54.830
It's not certain

23:54.830 --> 23:56.290
if we'll get into college.

23:58.160 --> 23:59.310
Besides,

24:00.070 --> 24:00.960
are you going to

24:01.880 --> 24:02.750
wait here

24:02.750 --> 24:03.680
for my response?

24:04.790 --> 24:06.110
If you keep waiting,

24:06.920 --> 24:08.440
I'll be bled dry again.

24:10.880 --> 24:12.210
You're right, Xiaolan.

24:12.440 --> 24:14.640
Let's talk when you're feeling better.

24:14.830 --> 24:15.490
Zhou Cheng.

24:19.590 --> 24:20.520
I dreamed of you.

24:23.480 --> 24:24.750
Besides dreaming of you,

24:24.750 --> 24:26.310
I also dreamt of my mom,

24:26.640 --> 24:27.590
my uncle,

24:28.030 --> 24:28.790
and my aunt-in-law—

24:28.790 --> 24:29.990
As long as I was there!

24:31.640 --> 24:32.770
That's good enough.

24:34.160 --> 24:34.770
Nurse,

24:34.920 --> 24:36.980
I need help to remove the needle here!

24:48.240 --> 24:50.160
I want to apply
to Huaqing's Architecture Department.

24:50.160 --> 24:51.620
It's a five-year program.

24:52.400 --> 24:54.330
You have to study for an extra year?

24:54.480 --> 24:56.740
That sounds really hard and impressive.

24:56.750 --> 24:57.550
Only our Xiaolan

24:57.550 --> 24:59.200
is smart enough for that.

25:00.550 --> 25:03.160
What does
this Architecture Department teach?

25:03.160 --> 25:03.560
Uncle.

25:03.780 --> 25:04.920
Simply put, it's...

25:04.920 --> 25:06.240
Sit down.

25:08.790 --> 25:09.640
Simply put,

25:09.920 --> 25:11.400
this major covers all

25:11.400 --> 25:13.260
skills related to architecture.

25:13.310 --> 25:14.880
From macro things like urban environments

25:14.880 --> 25:15.790
and building design,

25:15.790 --> 25:17.240
to micro things like family housing

25:17.240 --> 25:18.400
and interior design.

25:18.400 --> 25:19.240
You'll learn it all.

25:19.240 --> 25:20.960
Isn't that just building houses?

25:20.960 --> 25:22.750
Isn't that what I do?

25:23.030 --> 25:24.590
Do you really need to go to college

25:24.590 --> 25:25.390
to learn that?

25:25.720 --> 25:27.030
Uncle, relatively speaking...

25:27.030 --> 25:27.960
Sit down.

25:30.750 --> 25:32.350
Your work is more practical.

25:32.590 --> 25:33.680
What Xiaolan learns

25:33.680 --> 25:34.880
will be of a broader perspective.

25:34.880 --> 25:36.640
In the future, when you do renovations

25:36.640 --> 25:37.490
or build houses,

25:37.490 --> 25:38.720
you can ask Xiaolan to help you

25:38.720 --> 25:39.920
draw the blueprints.

25:41.510 --> 25:42.720
Do you understand?

25:43.070 --> 25:44.790
Xiaolan will be your boss.

25:45.030 --> 25:46.240
If you don't behave well,

25:46.240 --> 25:46.750
Xiaolan,

25:46.750 --> 25:47.680
punish him by sending him back

25:47.680 --> 25:48.940
to do farm work with me.

25:49.830 --> 25:50.560
Hello, Boss.

25:50.590 --> 25:51.030
Uncle.

25:52.400 --> 25:52.930
Xiaolan,

25:53.920 --> 25:55.720
the Architecture Department
is indeed very good.

25:55.720 --> 25:56.680
Huaqing's Architecture Department

25:56.680 --> 25:58.210
is top-tier in the country.

25:58.330 --> 25:59.980
But haven't you considered

26:00.070 --> 26:00.720
finance

26:00.880 --> 26:01.920
or economics?

26:02.310 --> 26:02.920
In the future,

26:02.920 --> 26:04.180
those will be booming.

26:05.030 --> 26:07.200
It's exactly because
I know those will boom

26:07.200 --> 26:08.750
that I want to study architecture

26:08.750 --> 26:09.950
to enter real estate.

26:12.010 --> 26:13.720
I'm already so good at doing business,

26:13.720 --> 26:15.180
do I still need to study it?

26:19.110 --> 26:20.790
Hurry up. Stop dawdling.

26:20.890 --> 26:22.350
I can make my own decision.

26:22.960 --> 26:23.680
Xiaolan!

26:24.750 --> 26:25.280
Xiaolan!

26:25.440 --> 26:25.960
Here!

26:30.880 --> 26:32.280
You have relatives over?

26:34.070 --> 26:36.140
I'll make it short.

26:36.860 --> 26:38.580
I want to ask you for help

26:38.880 --> 26:40.400
regarding Chen Qing's
university application.

26:40.400 --> 26:41.130
Originally,

26:41.240 --> 26:42.900
we wanted him to stay in Yunan,

26:43.030 --> 26:43.880
but he just told me

26:43.880 --> 26:45.400
he wants to apply
to a university in Jingcheng.

26:45.400 --> 26:46.790
I don't understand this stuff.

26:46.790 --> 26:47.590
You're smart.

26:47.880 --> 26:49.790
Help me with it.

26:50.550 --> 26:51.830
With his score,

26:51.960 --> 26:54.290
can he get into a university in Jingcheng?

26:58.160 --> 26:58.760
Mrs. Chen,

26:59.200 --> 27:01.510
Chen Qing's estimated score

27:01.590 --> 27:02.670
is over 500.

27:03.140 --> 27:03.940
The safest bet

27:04.030 --> 27:06.360
is still Yunan's University of Commerce.

27:06.590 --> 27:07.160
See?

27:07.400 --> 27:08.510
That's what I said.

27:09.070 --> 27:09.920
Actually, our family

27:09.920 --> 27:11.110
thinks so too.

27:11.310 --> 27:12.750
His grandpa asked around too.

27:12.750 --> 27:14.110
The University of Commerce is good.

27:14.110 --> 27:15.170
It's close to home,

27:15.240 --> 27:16.480
just 2 to 3 hours away.

27:16.920 --> 27:17.450
But he...

27:18.400 --> 27:18.960
Auntie.

27:19.750 --> 27:21.550
The school estimates the Tier 1 cutoff

27:21.550 --> 27:22.680
to be 460.

27:23.110 --> 27:24.440
If Chen Qing really scores

27:24.440 --> 27:25.680
over 500,

27:26.070 --> 27:26.720
universities in Jingcheng

27:26.720 --> 27:27.850
are worth a shot too.

27:31.640 --> 27:32.200
Auntie.

27:32.750 --> 27:34.270
Jingcheng is a big city.

27:34.480 --> 27:36.440
The people and things he'll see there

27:36.440 --> 27:38.770
will definitely be different from Yunan.

27:39.350 --> 27:39.810
Then...

27:40.380 --> 27:42.270
have you thought of
which university do you want to apply to?

27:42.270 --> 27:44.750
I want to apply to
Jingcheng University of Business and Economics.

27:44.750 --> 27:45.200
Xiaolan,

27:45.200 --> 27:46.530
do you know this school?

27:46.750 --> 27:47.270
I do.

27:47.720 --> 27:48.960
Jingcheng University of Business and Economics

27:48.960 --> 27:50.720
is the only

27:50.750 --> 27:52.240
key economic university in the country.

27:52.240 --> 27:53.030
Most of its majors

27:53.030 --> 27:54.550
are related to economics.

27:55.400 --> 27:56.550
International Economics and Trade

27:56.550 --> 27:57.680
is their best major.

27:58.000 --> 27:59.130
You can give it a try,

27:59.270 --> 28:01.260
but you should agree to reassignment.

28:01.260 --> 28:02.830
I'll definitely agree to reassignment.

28:02.830 --> 28:03.680
As for my second preference,

28:03.680 --> 28:05.340
I'll choose it carefully too.

28:05.440 --> 28:05.830
Mom,

28:05.900 --> 28:07.270
Xiaolan said so too.

28:07.270 --> 28:08.800
You should be relieved now.

28:09.750 --> 28:10.550
I'm relieved!

28:10.880 --> 28:12.280
Let's listen to Xiaolan.

28:13.350 --> 28:13.920
Xiaolan,

28:13.920 --> 28:15.440
the exams are over.

28:15.680 --> 28:16.220
During the summer break,

28:16.220 --> 28:17.820
you two should hang out more.

28:17.830 --> 28:19.240
When you go to Jingcheng,

28:19.790 --> 28:21.680
you'll need to look after each other.

28:21.680 --> 28:22.720
Listen up, boy.

28:23.030 --> 28:24.920
The responsibility
of looking after Xiaolan

28:24.920 --> 28:25.680
is yours now.

28:25.960 --> 28:27.000
You have to treat Xiaolan

28:27.000 --> 28:27.680
nicely.

28:27.830 --> 28:28.590
Mom.

28:31.070 --> 28:31.680
I...

28:32.690 --> 28:33.200
definitely will.

28:33.200 --> 28:34.070
He's blushing.

28:34.680 --> 28:35.790
What I just said

28:35.920 --> 28:37.030
is roughly what you need

28:37.030 --> 28:38.560
to learn for architecture.

28:38.920 --> 28:40.000
Look at that.

28:40.270 --> 28:42.160
No wonder it takes 5 years.

28:43.000 --> 28:44.350
It's not as simple as

28:44.350 --> 28:45.240
you roughnecks think.

28:45.240 --> 28:46.070
You guys chat.

28:47.160 --> 28:47.830
I'm going back to work.

28:47.830 --> 28:49.070
You think just mixing some lime

28:49.070 --> 28:50.550
and dirt is enough?

28:50.790 --> 28:52.120
Building small shacks?

28:54.720 --> 28:56.050
My mom is just like that.

28:57.640 --> 28:58.550
Chen Qing.

28:59.550 --> 29:01.550
There are things you've never said.

29:02.260 --> 29:03.350
What I'm about to say

29:03.350 --> 29:04.680
might be presumptuous,

29:04.880 --> 29:07.010
but I don't want you to misunderstand.

29:09.070 --> 29:11.000
We've been classmates
for over half a year.

29:11.000 --> 29:12.000
I've always felt

29:12.000 --> 29:13.660
a sincere friendship for you.

29:15.960 --> 29:17.020
Jingcheng is huge.

29:17.440 --> 29:18.970
College life is wonderful.

29:19.270 --> 29:20.420
I sincerely hope

29:20.640 --> 29:21.700
you will meet a girl

29:22.030 --> 29:23.090
who treats you well

29:23.160 --> 29:24.160
and likes you.

29:26.750 --> 29:27.550
I understand.

29:29.510 --> 29:30.170
I'll go back

29:30.240 --> 29:32.170
and fill out my application first.

29:39.200 --> 29:40.000
Ch-Chen Qing!

29:42.830 --> 29:44.090
Your house is that way.

29:56.480 --> 29:57.880
What are you smirking at?

29:59.070 --> 29:59.750
I was thinking about

29:59.750 --> 30:01.750
how you rejected Chen Qing just now.

30:01.920 --> 30:04.070
It seemed different
from when you rejected me.

30:04.070 --> 30:05.270
When you rejected me,

30:05.350 --> 30:06.550
you were more gentle.

30:06.720 --> 30:07.270
Yeah.

30:07.590 --> 30:08.510
I rejected you too.

30:08.510 --> 30:09.710
Why won't you give up?

30:10.100 --> 30:11.560
Because I'm not Chen Qing.

30:11.800 --> 30:13.000
Even if you reject me,

30:13.030 --> 30:13.890
I won't give up.

30:14.200 --> 30:15.920
I won't run away
with my tail between my legs.

30:15.920 --> 30:17.310
I'll go to Jingcheng, to Huaqing

30:17.310 --> 30:17.960
with you.

30:18.440 --> 30:19.750
As long as there's no one else,

30:19.750 --> 30:20.680
I have a chance.

30:22.400 --> 30:23.400
Mr. Zhou.

30:23.400 --> 30:24.930
Don't celebrate too early.

30:25.070 --> 30:26.640
If you don't get into Huaqing,

30:26.640 --> 30:27.900
I'll still reject you.

30:29.720 --> 30:29.960
Okay.

30:29.960 --> 30:31.160
Passengers bound for Jingcheng,

30:31.160 --> 30:33.000
please proceed
to ticket check immediately.

30:33.000 --> 30:33.880
Train's about to depart.

30:33.880 --> 30:35.200
I'm going in.

30:36.030 --> 30:36.960
Wait for my good news.

30:36.960 --> 30:37.350
Okay.

30:52.920 --> 30:53.360
Here.

30:58.590 --> 30:59.390
Safe travels.

31:14.410 --> 31:14.840
Uncle.

31:16.070 --> 31:16.800
You're back.

31:17.400 --> 31:18.960
Zhou Cheng left?

31:19.200 --> 31:19.640
Yes.

31:21.480 --> 31:22.030
Xiaolan.

31:25.720 --> 31:26.110
Sit.

31:29.510 --> 31:31.640
You're going to college soon.

31:32.400 --> 31:34.350
About Zhou Cheng,

31:35.240 --> 31:37.720
I want to give you some advice.

31:38.920 --> 31:39.480
Uncle.

31:40.200 --> 31:42.240
Zhou Cheng made some money

31:42.240 --> 31:43.440
doing logistics previously,

31:43.440 --> 31:44.900
but he quit a long time ago.

31:45.110 --> 31:45.640
Really?

31:46.070 --> 31:46.640
Really.

31:47.200 --> 31:48.160
He's just

31:48.160 --> 31:49.560
an ordinary student now.

31:52.270 --> 31:53.330
Then I'm relieved.

31:54.750 --> 31:56.680
If the kid walks the right path,

31:57.310 --> 31:58.040
that's good.

31:59.240 --> 32:00.920
I'm on the right path now too.

32:01.750 --> 32:03.640
I only do renovations now.

32:04.680 --> 32:05.790
Business at Blue Phoenix

32:05.790 --> 32:06.650
is very stable.

32:06.830 --> 32:08.760
I don't need to take risks anymore.

32:09.000 --> 32:10.350
But to be honest,

32:10.590 --> 32:12.990
speculating goods brings in money faster.

32:14.270 --> 32:14.830
Uncle.

32:15.510 --> 32:17.910
There are actually
many ways to make money.

32:18.030 --> 32:19.430
You're capable and bold,

32:19.480 --> 32:21.340
so you can definitely go further.

32:23.270 --> 32:24.200
Tell me about it.

32:25.440 --> 32:27.400
Do you know Shengcheng?

32:27.880 --> 32:28.920
Where you get the clothes—

32:28.920 --> 32:30.450
that place near Longcheng?

32:30.830 --> 32:32.270
I heard it from the radio—

32:32.550 --> 32:33.640
they call it a special zone, right?

32:33.640 --> 32:34.030
Yes.

32:34.830 --> 32:35.790
My old coworker,

32:35.790 --> 32:36.440
Fang,

32:36.440 --> 32:37.640
he's there right now.

32:38.110 --> 32:39.310
Right now in Shengcheng,

32:39.310 --> 32:41.310
new houses are going up everywhere.

32:41.440 --> 32:44.160
Where there are new houses,
there's renovation work.

32:44.160 --> 32:44.920
If others can run

32:44.920 --> 32:46.200
a whole renovation team,

32:46.200 --> 32:47.200
so can you, Uncle.

32:48.160 --> 32:49.090
You want me to go?

32:51.270 --> 32:52.350
Can I do it?

32:52.680 --> 32:53.110
Yes.

32:56.920 --> 32:57.550
I can't.

32:58.110 --> 32:59.680
Look at how things are now.

32:59.680 --> 33:01.140
With this big family here,

33:01.400 --> 33:02.350
if I leave,

33:02.510 --> 33:03.440
I won't be at ease.

33:03.440 --> 33:04.030
Uncle.

33:04.730 --> 33:05.850
A family should be

33:05.880 --> 33:07.140
each other's support.

33:07.310 --> 33:08.350
We shouldn't let worry

33:08.350 --> 33:09.480
hold us back.

33:09.960 --> 33:11.640
Mom and Auntie will do fine

33:11.750 --> 33:13.200
watching the clothing store.

33:13.200 --> 33:14.400
You can rest assured.

33:16.510 --> 33:17.510
As for me,

33:18.670 --> 33:20.270
when the exam results are out,

33:20.270 --> 33:21.530
I'll know what's next.

33:22.790 --> 33:23.650
Think about it.

33:31.070 --> 33:31.800
Shengcheng.

33:36.790 --> 33:37.200
Mom!

33:42.680 --> 33:43.480
Stop looking.

33:43.680 --> 33:44.700
I came back alone.

33:45.350 --> 33:46.350
Where is Jianhua?

33:46.510 --> 33:47.960
His parents were reinstated.

33:47.960 --> 33:49.820
Their house is bustling with guests,

33:49.820 --> 33:51.420
so he doesn't have much time.

33:53.340 --> 33:55.100
So, he's a city boy again?

33:55.550 --> 33:56.510
Does he look down on us

33:56.510 --> 33:57.960
for being country folk?

33:58.310 --> 33:58.880
Mom.

33:59.200 --> 34:00.070
I've made it to a university.

34:00.070 --> 34:01.240
I'm a city girl too.

34:01.720 --> 34:02.380
Well, if...

34:03.110 --> 34:04.840
if Xia Xiaolan passes the exam,

34:05.720 --> 34:07.120
she'll be a city girl too.

34:09.630 --> 34:10.360
Coming.

34:12.060 --> 34:12.620
Jianhua.

34:12.710 --> 34:13.150
Mom.

34:13.639 --> 34:14.159
Wang!

34:14.190 --> 34:15.000
Jianhua is back.

34:15.000 --> 34:15.400
Dad!

34:15.440 --> 34:15.960
Jianhua is here.

34:15.960 --> 34:17.000
Ziyu brought some gifts

34:17.000 --> 34:17.730
to visit you.

34:18.190 --> 34:19.190
Ziyu is here too?

34:19.510 --> 34:20.770
Hello, Uncle, Auntie.

34:21.280 --> 34:22.000
Wang.

34:23.510 --> 34:24.000
Bai!

34:24.280 --> 34:24.670
Hello.

34:24.670 --> 34:25.800
Come in, please.

34:26.280 --> 34:27.480
What brings you here?

34:29.000 --> 34:29.590
Jianhua,

34:30.000 --> 34:30.840
look, we have guests.

34:30.840 --> 34:32.900
Why don't you take Ziyu out for a walk?

34:53.440 --> 34:55.190
But her hand is injured.

34:55.760 --> 34:56.800
I heard that day,

34:56.800 --> 34:58.360
she went with a cast on.

34:58.890 --> 34:59.760
Even with that injury,

34:59.760 --> 35:01.020
she could still write.

35:04.710 --> 35:05.710
All right, let's not talk about her.

35:05.710 --> 35:06.570
Have you eaten?

35:06.710 --> 35:07.230
Not yet.

35:07.720 --> 35:08.440
Keep it down.

35:08.440 --> 35:09.770
Don't let Grandma know.

35:13.150 --> 35:14.610
The scores aren't out yet.

35:15.000 --> 35:16.660
I'm getting anxious waiting.

35:16.840 --> 35:17.800
We've been here since early morning.

35:17.800 --> 35:19.130
Why aren't they out yet?

35:19.550 --> 35:20.590
How long has it been?

35:19.880 --> 35:24.380
[Yunan Province Enrollment Office]

35:21.000 --> 35:23.320
This is
the Yunan Province Enrollment Office.

35:23.320 --> 35:24.530
The Province Enrolment Office

35:24.530 --> 35:27.190
has released
this year's admission cutoff scores.

35:27.190 --> 35:28.050
Here they come!

35:28.710 --> 35:29.840
Quick!

35:30.030 --> 35:30.960
The tier 1 cutoff score,

35:30.960 --> 35:33.290
and the associate degree cutoff score...

35:40.250 --> 35:41.000
The scores are out.

35:41.000 --> 35:42.530
The suspense is killing me.

35:46.800 --> 35:48.140
Key university cutoff is 494.

35:48.140 --> 35:50.000
Bachelor's degree cutoff is 460.

35:50.360 --> 35:51.230
What's the bachelor's degree cutoff?

35:51.230 --> 35:51.920
460?

35:52.840 --> 35:53.400
Qi,

35:53.800 --> 35:54.760
judging by your reaction,

35:54.760 --> 35:55.670
Anqing No.1 High School

35:55.670 --> 35:58.070
must have estimated good scores this year.

35:58.550 --> 35:59.360
460...

36:00.190 --> 36:01.920
Why isn't the top score out yet?

36:02.030 --> 36:03.480
I heard the gap between
the top score and second place

36:03.480 --> 36:04.230
is too big,

36:04.440 --> 36:05.320
so they're rechecking it.

36:05.320 --> 36:05.880
Too big?

36:06.110 --> 36:07.040
How big can it be?

36:24.800 --> 36:25.840
It's not broken.

36:25.920 --> 36:26.440
Why hasn't Ms. Qi

36:26.440 --> 36:27.590
called yet?

36:32.750 --> 36:33.440
Mr. Sun.

36:35.670 --> 36:36.590
Didn't I tell you?

36:36.590 --> 36:37.360
I'm waiting for a call.

36:37.360 --> 36:38.630
Don't bother me unless it's important.

36:38.630 --> 36:40.550
It's time for the graduation photo.

36:40.550 --> 36:42.110
I guess we have to take that.

36:49.590 --> 36:50.110
Come on, let's take the photo.

36:50.110 --> 36:51.510
Gather around, quickly.

36:52.360 --> 36:53.070
Come on, stand still.

36:53.070 --> 36:53.710
We're taking the picture.

36:53.710 --> 36:54.190
Come on.

36:54.440 --> 36:55.230
Hurry up.

36:55.880 --> 36:56.410
Xiaolan.

36:57.030 --> 36:58.630
Stand behind me. Right here.

36:59.030 --> 36:59.480
Come.

37:04.670 --> 37:05.730
Is everyone ready?

37:05.760 --> 37:06.440
Ready.

37:07.320 --> 37:08.650
Stand still, everyone.

37:09.400 --> 37:11.230
Students over there, squeeze in a bit.

37:11.230 --> 37:11.840
Good.

37:12.480 --> 37:13.360
Look here.

37:14.390 --> 37:16.880
3, 2, 1.

37:19.590 --> 37:21.030
The youth of an 18-year-old

37:21.030 --> 37:22.560
is captured in this moment.

37:22.960 --> 37:24.290
This bright exuberance

37:24.710 --> 37:26.840
belongs to the Xia Xiaolan of the past,

37:27.070 --> 37:29.400
and to the me of the present.

37:30.030 --> 37:31.280
It's out! It's out!

37:35.000 --> 37:35.630
How much

37:35.630 --> 37:36.380
did the top science scorer score?

37:36.380 --> 37:37.910
Which school are they from?

37:38.150 --> 37:39.410
Quiet down, everyone.

37:39.850 --> 37:40.880
Because the top science student

37:40.880 --> 37:41.630
and the second place

37:41.630 --> 37:43.110
have a 45-point gap...

37:44.050 --> 37:44.890
45 points?

37:44.920 --> 37:45.520
That much?

37:45.760 --> 37:46.480
To be cautious,

37:46.480 --> 37:48.000
we rechecked the scores.

37:48.400 --> 37:50.840
Two teachers reviewed each subject.

37:51.000 --> 37:53.000
The scores are absolutely correct.

37:54.400 --> 37:55.920
This year's top science student

37:55.920 --> 37:56.960
with 616 points

37:57.040 --> 37:58.370
is from Anqing County.

37:58.400 --> 37:59.440
Math was so hard this year.

37:59.440 --> 38:00.320
That's higher than last year's top scorer

38:00.320 --> 38:01.320
by over 30 points.

38:01.480 --> 38:02.290
Exactly.

38:02.320 --> 38:03.880
I can't believe
they're not from the province capital.

38:03.880 --> 38:04.960
A school from Anqing?

38:04.960 --> 38:06.190
Is it No.1 High School or No.2?

38:06.190 --> 38:06.590
Yeah.

38:06.630 --> 38:07.690
Which school is it?

38:07.840 --> 38:10.970
Is the province top scorer
from Anqing No.1 High School?

38:11.670 --> 38:12.510
Qi.

38:12.840 --> 38:14.360
Are you crazy?

38:14.670 --> 38:16.190
How many students
from Anqing No.1 High School

38:16.190 --> 38:17.800
can even get into college in a year?

38:17.800 --> 38:19.860
And you expect a province top scorer?

38:20.360 --> 38:21.070
Excuse me.

38:21.440 --> 38:23.500
Are you from Anqing No.1 High School?

38:26.030 --> 38:26.440
Yes.

38:26.710 --> 38:27.280
I am.

38:31.070 --> 38:32.510
Hello? Qi?

38:33.150 --> 38:33.710
Go ahead.

38:39.630 --> 38:40.030
You...

38:40.550 --> 38:42.250
Say that again.

38:49.880 --> 38:50.680
That's great!

38:51.480 --> 38:52.540
That's wonderful!

38:52.750 --> 38:53.800
616 points.

38:56.150 --> 38:57.190
616 points.

38:58.320 --> 38:59.480
616 points!

39:02.400 --> 39:03.670
616 points.

39:04.070 --> 39:05.110
Anqing No.1 High School

39:05.110 --> 39:06.440
has finally made it!

39:07.000 --> 39:08.000
Xia Xiaolan,

39:08.280 --> 39:10.000
you scored 616 points.

39:10.400 --> 39:12.960
You're
the province top scorer in science!

39:34.190 --> 39:35.550
Today we celebrate

39:35.880 --> 39:37.940
Xia Xiaolan becoming the top scorer.

39:38.780 --> 39:40.040
With your exam permit,

39:40.070 --> 39:41.400
you get a free fried egg.

39:42.120 --> 39:43.380
With your exam permit,

39:43.400 --> 39:44.960
you get a free fried egg.

39:43.500 --> 39:45.180
[To congratulate Xia Xiaolan on becoming the province top scorer,
we are giving away free fried eggs]

39:44.960 --> 39:45.590
Come on!

39:49.930 --> 39:51.710
[Closed]

39:57.660 --> 40:02.780
[Congratulations to Xia Xiaolan on becoming
the 84th province top science scorer with 616 points]

40:38.590 --> 40:39.450
Reporters,

40:39.760 --> 40:41.510
this is this year's province top scorer,

40:41.510 --> 40:42.590
Xia Xiaolan.

40:43.760 --> 40:45.190
The top scorer is quite pretty.

40:45.190 --> 40:46.150
She looks quite young.

40:46.150 --> 40:46.590
Yeah.

40:46.840 --> 40:48.340
Didn't they say
she dropped out for a few years?

40:48.340 --> 40:49.840
I thought she was in her 20s.

40:49.840 --> 40:50.590
Reporters,

40:50.590 --> 40:51.510
don't just stand there.

40:51.510 --> 40:52.600
If you have questions,

40:52.600 --> 40:53.700
ask Xiaolan directly.

40:53.700 --> 40:54.060
Okay.

40:54.090 --> 40:55.350
Okay, let us get ready.

40:59.360 --> 41:00.490
From this moment on,

41:01.280 --> 41:02.800
my golden age here

41:03.880 --> 41:05.000
is about to begin.
